headline: 2 Unstoppable Growth Stocks to Buy and Hold for 20 Years
summary: Getting rich in the stock market is simply a matter of patiently holding shares of growing companies over many years.  Here are two easy-to-understand companies you can buy today that can deliver massive returns over the next 20 years.  Dutch Bros (NYSE: BROS) was founded in 1992 and has grown to 982 locations with $1.3 billion in trailing revenue.
